'''Sith Minion''' was a rank of the [[Sith/Legends|Sith Order]] before [[Darth Bane/Legends|Darth Bane's]] [[Rule of Two/Legends|reform]]. They were the lowliest members of the Sith Order. They were often not even [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitive]], and sometimes worshiped the Sith Lords as gods. Sith Cultists can be considered examples of Sith Minions.

